{"TopicId":185208,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Helmets in IVA?","CreatedByName":"Rover 6428","CreatedById":184753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-06T19:45:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rover 6428","CreatedById":184753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-06T19:45:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EMy kerbals don\u0027t wear their helmets in IVA, and I wonder if there is a way to fix that.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JERONIMO","CreatedById":188491,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-07T04:09:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif my brain say the truth, IVA is when you are out of craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nok, if you are on Kerbin, there is a thing whe nyou right click called put a helmet. same on laythe.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif you are in space... proobably just a bug.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif it means in\u00A0vehicle activity, than everything is correct.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-07T04:26:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223613722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185208\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559880574\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JERONIMO\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, JERONIMO said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif my brain say the truth, IVA is when you are out of craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is EVA. Extravehicular Activity, not IVA\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-07T04:27:43Z\u0022 title=\u002206/07/2019 04:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 7, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by The_Cat_In_Space\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ussoldier2002","CreatedById":149741,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-16T22:17:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I would like my astronauts to be wearing their helmets during launch and landing as well. Not just on EVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JERONIMO","CreatedById":188491,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-16T22:23:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223620084\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185208\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221560723463\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149741\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ussoldier2002\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, ussoldier2002 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I would like my astronauts to be wearing their helmets during launch and landing as well. Not just on EVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell that\u0027s impossible \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ussoldier2002","CreatedById":149741,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-17T09:22:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223620087\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185208\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221560723781\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188491\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JERONIMO\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, JERONIMO said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell that\u0027s impossible \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is? I remember back in the day there was a mod that removed helmets. The mod would remove helmets \u0022in a safe environment\u0022 and they would not have helmets on but as soon as you lifted off the helmets would be on. It was weird but I didn\u0027t pay much attention to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JERONIMO","CreatedById":188491,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-17T22:27:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223620302\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185208\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221560763367\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149741\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ussoldier2002\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, ussoldier2002 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is? I remember back in the day there was a mod that removed helmets. The mod would remove helmets \u0022in a safe environment\u0022 and they would not have helmets on but as soon as you lifted off the helmets would be on. It was weird but I didn\u0027t pay much attention to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nummmm i think you talk about \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E, but it is possible only in atmosphere and in EVA. Now we have for this a great 1.6 (1.5???) KSP version \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-20T05:37:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223613445\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185208\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559850356\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rover 6428\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/6/2019 at 12:45 PM, Rover 6428 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EMy kerbals don\u0027t wear their helmets in IVA, and I wonder if there is a way to fix that.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think there is a definition in the INTERNAL node that determines whether and what type of helmet they wear.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIirc, they wear a fishbowl helmet only in the cupola.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OHara","CreatedById":162784,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-20T06:27:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have not tested it, but this Module Manager patch uses a setting that is still in the documented API so should still work:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022137442\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8418832813\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/172379-hats-on/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3323877\u0026amp;embedComment=3323877\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022 style=\u0022height:267px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: As written, the patch has effect only with certain pods, but you can change the\u00A0first line to @INTERNAL[*] to affect all parts with an IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-20T06:31:23Z\u0022 title=\u002206/20/2019 06:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 20, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by OHara\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}